                <u>Thought: </u> <br> Education is not the learning of facts but training of the mind to think!<br> Being science enthusiats ourselves, we realise that real science isn't just for classrooms but is a part of everyday life. <br><br> To
                make students 'feel' science, we organised "Shiksha weekends" for the students of Pandit Awadh Bihar Devideen Shiksha Niketan, Kanpur Dehat from the first weekend of April, 2022. The main aim of this endeavour was to make science (particularly,
                physics) fun and simple!
            </p>
